metadata.name: Andromeda
metadata.description:
"Andromeda"

The future will change the world....

The future will save from revenge and envy ....

The future will heal the wounds of the past...

The future of new people...

Andromeda - the main star of the pilgrim cyborg universe

She sacrificed herself for an experiment in a science lab
combining biological and mechanical principles.

She became a new source of light in another world, the world of technology.
